	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok I have seen many things on these posts regarding which Crystal Silks to use for the quest....so i tried it.  I went to Crystal Caverns and dropped down to the tunnel leading to the city (a good place to camp orcs BTW)  I killed 5 orcs and had my Vellium pieces (3) and the Blocks of Vellium.  Next I headed down to the area where the spiders spawn and pulled spiders to the entrance to the Geonid Hallway leading to the exit of the zone (another good place to camp spiders and Terrors BTW)  I got 3 Crystal Silks (do not use the Crystal Webs, they are unstackable so you can tell the difference)  Gated back to Thuragin and sat at the pottery wheel.  I followed the quest guidlines and created the unfired vial of velium, then proceeded to the kiln which produced the Vial of Vellium.  I headed to the gal who gives the purifier and followed the quest guidelines and combined the vial in the purifier to make the Velium Vapors.  A friend and I both did this at the same time...so I KNOW FOR FACT that the Silks from Crystal Caverns work.  For those who dont believe.....go ahead...step in Velk's Lab and spend hour after hour killing those HARD spiders....in the meantime ill have all my chars with shawls because Crystal Caverns is uncamped 8)<br><br>Good Luck!<br>&nbsp;<br>Beebe Lytcaster 51 Necromancer<br>Hiyeedi Fliess 54 Druid<br>~Rallos Zek~</td></tr>
