	   <tr><td colspan=2>Thought I would let everyone in on the how to find the trigger for Tanik or the Death Squad.<br>First what you need to do is make a pet, or find someone who can make one for you.  You need to make the pet at the top of the ramp to Keal.  Now have the pet guard that loc. ( /pet guard here ) The pet will face a direction.  now you need to see where the pet is pointing and then walk in that direction with the pet following you (/pet follow me )  take 10 steps and repeat the pet guard command. Your pet will point you in the direction you need to go to walk over the trigger.  If this doesn't make sence just try it and you will see.  Make sure you have SoW or FD cause the Giants spawn more times then Tanik will.  Good hunting!!!!<br><br><br>Sollaen Magikos<br>50th Magician<br>Torvonnilous server<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
