<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=99036732750930></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f99036732750930><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj><a href=/quest.html?quest=1240&mid=99036732750930 style='color: darkblue;'>Tanik</a></span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id=>Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sun, May 20th 10:02 AM</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>This is the method that worked for me.<br><br>Go to the bottom of the ramp- getting as close to the double pillars as possible without aggroing the giants.<br><br>Now start at one wall, and cross the ramp.  When you get to the other side, come back across in the other direction, moving slightly up the ramp to cover a bit more ground.<br><br>By going back and forth across the ramp in a "zig-zag" you cover all the ground there.  Eventually, i got tanik to spawn - twice using this method since the first time i blew it.  hehe.<br><br>hope that helps.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
