	   <tr><td colspan=2>Kal, Tanik spawns down close to where the giants are lurking behind the posts just outside the doorway to the fortress.   You're far down on the ramp, not at all near the middle or top.  I was able to find him twice right away while doing this quest for myself and a friend.  Each time Tanik spawned immediately as I approached the entrance a little to the right of the doorway, as if to walk up to that support post...try pacing around that area, just be careful not to agro the giants.  Hope this helps!<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
